settings.custom_liquid:
{% comment %}
  Template: Shipping & Delivery
  This page provides details about shipping options, delivery times, costs, and tracking.
{% endcomment %}

<div class="shipping-delivery-container">
  <h1>Shipping & Delivery</h1>

  <section class="shipping-section">
    <h2>Shipping Methods & Delivery Times</h2>
    <p>We offer reliable and fast shipping to ensure your orders reach you on time.</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Standard Shipping:</strong> 5-7 business days</li>
      <li><strong>Express Shipping:</strong> 2-3 business days</li>
      <li><strong>Overnight Shipping:</strong> Next-day delivery</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section class="shipping-section">
    <h2>Shipping Costs</h2>
    <p>Shipping costs are calculated at checkout based on your location and selected shipping method.</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Standard Shipping:</strong> Free on orders above ₹999, otherwise ₹50</li>
      <li><strong>Express Shipping:</strong> ₹150</li>
      <li><strong>Overnight Shipping:</strong> ₹300</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section class="shipping-section">
    <h2>International Shipping</h2>
    <p>We ship worldwide! International shipping rates and delivery times vary by country.</p>
    <p>For international shipping inquiries, please email us at <a href="mailto:trezon.in@gmail.com">trezon.in@gmail.com</a></p>
  </section>

  <section class="shipping-section">
    <h2>Order Tracking</h2>
    <p>Once your order is shipped, you will receive a tracking link via email. You can also track your order on our <a href="/pages/track-order">Track Your Order</a> page.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="shipping-section">
    <h2>Need Help?</h2>
    <p>If you have any questions, feel free to contact our customer support at <a href="mailto:trezon.in@gmail.com">trezon.in@gmail.com</a></p>
  </section>
</div>

<style>
  .shipping-delivery-container {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 20px;
    background: #EEDFA4; /* Background color */
    border-radius: 10px;
  }
  .shipping-section {
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  .shipping-section h2 {
    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: bold;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }
  .shipping-section p, .shipping-section ul {
    font-size: 16px;
    color: #333;
  }
  .shipping-section ul {
    list-style-type: disc;
    margin-left: 20px;
  }
  .shipping-section a {
    color: #392D00;
    font-weight: bold;
    text-decoration: none;
  }
  .shipping-section a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }
</style>
